00:15:57.750 --> 00:16:00.670
♪To cross over the high wall♪

00:16:02.390 --> 00:16:05.790
♪Waiting for the shore♪

00:16:06.550 --> 00:16:10.350
♪To forget the storm♪

00:16:11.470 --> 00:16:14.990
♪Just like this♪

00:16:15.790 --> 00:16:19.190
♪Wasting a few inches♪

00:16:19.190 --> 00:16:20.510
♪Of daylight♪

00:16:20.750 --> 00:16:23.910
♪Half for the memories♪

00:16:25.390 --> 00:16:29.270
♪Half for the dreams♪

00:16:29.870 --> 00:16:31.950
♪Oh, little boat♪

00:16:32.150 --> 00:16:34.270
♪Where are you going♪

00:16:34.670 --> 00:16:38.550
♪No need to answer that♪

00:16:39.070 --> 00:16:41.270
♪Just let me♪

00:16:41.470 --> 00:16:43.510
♪Watch you drift away♪

00:16:43.510 --> 00:16:47.710
♪Into the sunset glow♪

00:16:48.270 --> 00:16:50.430
♪Don't be afraid♪

00:16:50.630 --> 00:16:52.750
♪This world♪

00:16:52.990 --> 00:16:57.030
♪Is vast as it may be♪

00:16:57.630 --> 00:16:59.910
♪But there's always♪

00:16:59.910 --> 00:17:01.910
♪Someone who cares♪

00:17:01.910 --> 00:17:05.870
♪Shining like a lighthouse♪